title: The Shattering
subTitle: Donovan lures several friends into the woods to meet a healer with his cancer-stricken girlfriend. Lucy. As they are hunted by creatures and commandos, the friends realize they were set up to pay for Lucy's cure.

subTitle: A deranged fan holds the star of a classic '80s horror movie captive in her home until he falls in love with her.

title: Death's Door
subTitle: A dozen young men and women have a party in a dilapidated mansion. When it's time to go, all of the exits are blocked and the people become trapped.

title: Chopping Block
subTitle: Several corporate guys are laid off and make a plan to kidnap their boss's daughter to ransom her. Their plan takes a bloody turn when they grab her and unwittingly rescue her from a masked psychopath.

subTitle: A man (Patrick Barnitt) sees live footage of his estranged wife and her lover (Kevin Sorbo) trapped in a pine box.

subTitle: Trick is among five hostages who are trapped together and paralyzed from the neck down. An FBI agent and a former detective race against the clock to find them before their promised execution is carried out.
